## 1. PROJECT SUMMARY

**Name:** catat-app
**Type:** Mobile application (Android-first)
**Domain:** Small accommodation business management (guest houses, kos, penginapan)

### Problem
Small accommodation owners in Indonesia manage bookings manually — via WhatsApp, physical notebooks, or Excel — leading to double bookings, lost payment records, and no clear reporting.

### Solution
A lightweight, low-cost mobile app that centralizes bookings, customers, payments, and room availability using Google's free ecosystem (Sheets, Calendar, Drive) as the backend infrastructure.

### Target Users
- Non-technical accommodation owners and staff
- Single-property or small multi-room operations (2–30 rooms)
- Indonesian market (KTP/NIK as customer identifier)

### Key Value Propositions
- Zero backend hosting cost (Google ecosystem only)
- OCR from KTP photo — no manual customer data entry
- Google Calendar sync — visual availability at a glance
- PDF invoice/receipt generation on-device
- Works on any Android phone with internet access

