### Relationships
```
users ──────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │                                             │
  │ created_by                    created_by   │
  ▼                                             ▼
transactions ◄──── customer_id ──── customers  payments
     │                                            ▲
     │ room_id                                   │
     ▼                          transaction_id  │
   rooms                            ────────────┘
```

### Business Rules (enforced in Apps Script)
- NIK must be 16 digits and unique in `customers`
- Booking code auto-incremented per day: `BK-20260402-001`
- `payment_status` auto-updated on payment creation:
  - `sum(payments.amount) == 0` → `unpaid`
  - `0 < sum < total_price` → `partial`
  - `sum >= total_price` → `paid`
- Room cannot be double-booked (check overlap before insert)

