## 6. SYSTEM FLOWS

### Flow 1: Login
```
User opens app
  → Splash screen checks shared_preferences for cached user
  → [Cached] → Go to Dashboard
  → [Not cached] → Show Google Sign-In button
      → Tap Sign In → google_sign_in.signIn()
      → Get idToken
      → POST { action: "auth.login", token: idToken }
      → Apps Script: verify token via tokeninfo endpoint
      → [Invalid] → Return 401 → Show error
      → [Valid] → Upsert user in users sheet → Return user object
      → Flutter: save user to shared_preferences → Go to Dashboard
```

### Flow 2: Booking Creation (with OCR + Calendar)
```
Tap "New Booking"
  → Select room from dropdown
  → Pick check-in / check-out dates
  → System shows: nights count + total price
  → Customer section:
      → [Search by NIK] → GET customers.getByNIK
          → [Found] → Pre-fill customer fields (read-only)
          → [Not found] → Enable "Scan KTP" or "Add Manually"
              → Scan KTP:
                  → image_picker (camera)
                  → ML Kit text recognition → raw text
                  → Regex parser extracts: NIK, name, address, birth_date
                  → Show editable form pre-filled with OCR results
                  → User confirms/corrects fields
  → Input phone number
  → Input down payment (optional)
  → Tap "Save Booking"
      → Apps Script:
          → Acquire LockService
          → Check room availability (no overlapping active transactions)
          → [Conflict] → Return 409 → Show "Room not available" error
          → [Available]:
              → If new customer: create customer record, upload KTP to Drive
              → Generate booking_code
              → Create transaction record
              → Create Google Calendar event via CalendarApp
              → Store calendar_event_id in transaction
              → Release lock
              → Return transaction object
      → Flutter: show success screen with booking_code
      → Option: generate and share Invoice PDF
```

### Flow 3: Payment Update
```
Open Transaction Detail
  → Tap "Add Payment"
  → Input: amount, method, date, notes
  → POST { action: "payments.create", data: { transaction_id, amount, ... } }
      → Apps Script:
          → Acquire LockService
          → Insert payment record
          → Recalculate sum of all payments for transaction
          → Update transactions.payment_status accordingly
          → Release lock
          → Return updated transaction
  → Flutter: refresh transaction detail
  → Option: generate Receipt (Kwitansi) PDF if fully paid
```

### Flow 4: Reporting
```
Dashboard loads
  → POST { action: "reports.summary", data: { from, to } }
      → Apps Script:
          → Filter transactions by date range
          → Aggregate: count bookings, sum total_price, sum payments
          → Group by day/week/month based on range
          → Return structured summary object
  → Flutter: render charts and summary cards

Export CSV:
  → Tap "Export"
  → POST { action: "reports.export", data: { from, to, format: "csv" } }
      → Apps Script:
          → Fetch filtered transactions + customer + room joins
          → Build CSV string
          → Return as base64 encoded string
  → Flutter: decode → save to Downloads → share via Android share sheet
```

