## 7. API DESIGN

All requests: `POST <APPS_SCRIPT_WEB_APP_URL>`
All bodies: `{ "action": "<action>", "token": "<google_id_token>", "data": { ... } }`
All responses: `{ "success": true|false, "data": { ... }, "error": "message", "timestamp": "ISO8601" }`

### Auth
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `auth.login` | token | user object |

### Customers
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `customers.list` | — | array of customers |
| `customers.getByNIK` | `{ nik }` | customer or null |
| `customers.create` | customer fields + ktp_base64 | created customer |
| `customers.update` | `{ id, ...fields }` | updated customer |
| `customers.delete` | `{ id }` | success |

### Rooms
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `rooms.list` | — | array of rooms |
| `rooms.create` | room fields | created room |
| `rooms.update` | `{ id, ...fields }` | updated room |
| `rooms.delete` | `{ id }` | success |

### Transactions
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `transactions.list` | `{ from?, to?, status? }` | array of transactions |
| `transactions.getById` | `{ id }` | transaction + customer + room |
| `transactions.create` | all transaction fields | created transaction |
| `transactions.update` | `{ id, ...fields }` | updated transaction |
| `transactions.delete` | `{ id }` | success |
| `transactions.checkAvailability` | `{ room_id, check_in, check_out, exclude_id? }` | `{ available: bool }` |

### Payments
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `payments.create` | `{ transaction_id, amount, method, paid_at, notes }` | payment + updated transaction status |
| `payments.listByTransaction` | `{ transaction_id }` | array of payments |
| `payments.delete` | `{ id }` | success + recalculated transaction status |

### Reports
| Action | Input | Output |
|---|---|---|
| `reports.summary` | `{ from, to }` | `{ total_bookings, total_income, paid_count, partial_count, unpaid_count, series[] }` |
| `reports.export` | `{ from, to }` | `{ csv_base64: string, filename: string }` |

