## 9. FUTURE IMPROVEMENTS

### Short-term (after v1.0)
- Push notifications for upcoming check-ins (Firebase Cloud Messaging)
- WhatsApp message template for booking confirmation (`wa.me` deep link)
- Offline read-only mode (local SQLite cache)
- Multi-language support (English + Bahasa Indonesia)
- Barcode/QR scanner for NIK lookup

### Medium-term
- Multi-property support (multiple Sheets, property selector)
- Staff role permissions (staff cannot delete, cannot see full reports)
- Photo gallery per room
- Recurring booking support (weekly/monthly)
- Custom invoice template (property logo, colors)

### Long-term / Migration Path
- Migrate to Firebase Firestore when >30 rooms or >100 bookings/month
- Web dashboard companion (Flutter Web or Next.js)
- Payment gateway integration (Midtrans/Xendit for online payments)
- Channel manager sync (Booking.com, Traveloka)

